title: The Extra is Too Strong
summary: The Extra is Too Strong Manhwa I received the same question every day, but the answer never changed. The only things I had left were sympathetic gazes and the monthly insurance payments. And the cruel reality of being half-paralyzed. They say that God only gives you trials you can endure, but I would rather have died. That was when I woke up— [This is the world of the “Magician Who Dominates the World.”] [From now on, you must live as the character “Mord Vernars.”] I became an extra in the novel I was reading overnight. 엑스트라가 너무 강함,
